<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>ترتيبها ٦٨ ... سُورَةُ القَلَمِ ... آياتها ٥٢ ... مكية<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>الآية ... الكلمة ... معناها<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَالْقَلَمِ}</span> ... قَسَمٌ بِالقَلَمِ الَّذِي تَكْتُبُ بِهِ المَلَائِكَةُ، وَالنَّاسُ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَمَا يَسْطُرُونَ}</span> ... وَالَّذِي يَكْتُبُونَهُ بِالقَلَمِ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مَمْنُونٍ}</span> ... مَنْقُوصٍ، وَلَا مُنْقَطِعٍ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{بِأَييِّكُمُ الْمَفْتُونُ}</span> ... فَي أَيِّ الفَرِيقَيْنِ الفِتْنَةُ، وَالجُنُونُ؟<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{تُدْهِنُ}</span> ... تُلَايِنُ، وَتُصَانِعُ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(١٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{حَلَّافٍ}</span> ... كَثِيرِ الحَلِفِ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(١٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مَّهِينٍ}</span> ... كَذَّابٍ، حَقِيرٍ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(١١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{هَمَّازٍ}</span> ... مُغْتَابٍ لِلنَّاسِ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(١١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مَّشَّاءٍ بِنَمِيمٍ}</span> ... يَمْشِي بِالنَّمِيمَةِ،<span class="c5"> وَهِيَ:</span> نَقْلُ الحَدِيثِ بَيْنَ النَّاسِ عَلَى وَجْهِ الإِفْسَادِ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(١٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{عُتُلٍّ}</span> ... فَاحِشٍ، لَئِيمٍ، غَلِيظٍ فيِ كُفْرِهِ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c2">(١٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{زَنِيمٍ}</span> ... مَنْسُوبٍ لِغَيْرِ أَبِيهِ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c2">(١٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أَن كَانَ}</span> ... مِنْ أَجْلِ أَنَّهُ كَانَ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c2">(١٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أَسَاطِيرُ الْأَوَّلِينَ}</span> ... أَبَاطِيلُهُمْ، وَخُرَافَاتُهُمْ.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span class="c2">(١٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{سَنَسِمُهُ}</span> ... سَنَجْعَلُ لَهُ عَلَامَةً لَا تُفَارِقُهُ.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span><span class="c2">(١٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الْخُرْطُومِ}</span> ... أَنْفِهِ.<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>